query:
UPDATE address 
        SET 
            tara = $2,
            judet = $3,
            localitate = $4,
            cod_postal = $5,
            strada = $6,
            numar = $7,
            bloc = $8,
            scara = $9,
            etaj = $10,
            apartament = $11,
            updated_at = NOW()
        WHERE uuid = $1
